{"tid":1344733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你有權簽身分證 我有權查委任證","createTime":"2019-07-22T00:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T00:27:41.000Z","uid":157015,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5784ee8059404b040d463a0f2d0b9018869814","tid":1344733,"uid":157015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:21:27.000Z","msg":"如有疑似冒警 我地要盡公民責任<br />\n&ldquo;麻煩出示委任證&rdquo;<br />\n為方便日後執法 過程必須錄影<br />\n<br />\n（二）如市民提出要求，軍裝警務人員須出示委任證，除了三種情況。第一是「情況不容許」出示；或第二是「出示委任證會影響警隊行動及/或危及有關人員的安全」；或第三是「要求不合理」。(PGO 20-16)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/822/chi/f01.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F822%2Fchi%2Ff01.htm&d=D9%2BIkncl4BF5lZ8wPV9kyDYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=51e727a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/822/chi/f01.htm</a>"},{"pid":"00101be8af78416c0a028d0ce72d283322a61d95","tid":1344733,"uid":157015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:22:05.000Z","msg":"黑警可㤈"},{"pid":"cf06f0448280b55298c957558c0bcd26c0a7a24b","tid":1344733,"uid":157015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:22:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2877d3b2ba907190fa293755979f3b52fe64b13c","tid":1344733,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:22:41.000Z","msg":"建制派及其政府 公然向香港市民發動恐怖襲擊！"},{"pid":"ef4e55e018d8d6749885ea8b5306a962ba95048a","tid":1344733,"uid":157015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:23:00.000Z","msg":"我要查你委任證"},{"pid":"9a8f775382e337123f725a24e826ce56bb884bd5","tid":1344733,"uid":157015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:23:55.000Z","msg":"我要做好市民"},{"pid":"a6616a1f80290123328deb3b4c97121c3546d8dd","tid":1344733,"uid":157015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:24:31.000Z","msg":"麻煩出示委任證"},{"pid":"7d7f6c4e0fa8bcd4600a950b6af57b69dd1e31d6","tid":1344733,"uid